short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension to solve Sudoku

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You can input your sudoku problem by inserting the numbers in the given sudoku cells and then click on the solve button the solution will be displayed. You can also use this to create new sudoku , just put random numbers into the cells while following sudoku rules and then press solve.
